estyle/esmagazine/suzannah-lipscombs-my-london-8985703.html | title=Suzannah Lipscomb's My London | work=[[Evening Standard]] | location= London|date=6 December 2013 | accessdate=26 May 2015 | author=Nathanson, Hannah}}</ref>||[[File:Suzannah Lipscomb 2013.jpg|120px]]\n|-\n|[[George MacKay (actor)|George MacKay]]|| b. 1992|| Actor||Grew up in Barnes||<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://barnesfilmfestival.wordpress.com/2016/06/24/welcome-patron-george-mackay/|title=Welcome Patron George MacKay|date=2016-06-24|website=Barnes Film Festival Blog|language=en|access-date=2020-01-31}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/features/george-mackay-interview-nhs-to-provide-all-people-secret-of-marrowbone-a8417786.html|title='I\u2019m trying to be more political': George MacKay on how acting in NHS drama To Provide All People was a wake-up call|date=26 June 2018|work=[[The Independent]]|author= Aftab, Kaleem|language=en|access-date=31 January 2020}}</ref>||[[File:GeorgeMackaySept2013TIFF.jpg|120px]]\n|-\n|Dr [[Tania Mathias]]||b. 1964|| MP for Twickenham<br/> from 2015 to 2017||Brought up in Barnes||<ref name=introduction>{{cite news |url=http://www.richmondandtwickenhamtimes.co.uk/news/12952640.Meet_Tania_Mathias__Your_new_MP_for_Twickenham/ |title=Meet Tania Mathias: Your new MP for Twickenham |work=[[Richmond and Twickenham Times]] |date=15 May 2015 |accessdate=17 May 2015 |url-status = dead|df=dmy-all |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150717143401/http://www.richmondandtwickenhamtimes.co.uk/news/12952640.Meet_Tania_Mathias__Your_new_MP_for_Twickenham/ |archive-date=17 July 2015 }}</ref>||[[File:Tania Mathias Headshot.jpg|120px]]\n|-\n|[[Brian May]]|| b. 1947|| Musician, singer, songwriter<br/> and astrophysicist||Has lived at Suffolk Road, Barnes||<ref name = \"Queen\">{{cite web|author=Sk\u00e1la, Martin|url=http://www.queenconcerts.com/london.html |title=Queen places in London |publisher=Queen Concerts |date= |accessdate=12 April 2